{
  "stem": "10446.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was an incredible experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, of course, slowly we found out that relatives of ours had been exterminated, killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were extremely fortunate that close relatives had not been affected, but parents of cousins of mine were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One, two, three couples were sent to Riga.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And people in Riga were put into a concentration camp outside the city and were shot on short order.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They, they didn't last long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] another couple was killed right where they lived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was not immediate family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was cousin-- parents of cousins, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of course, which was bad enough.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was absolutely incredible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was incredible that something like that happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was incredible to, to us that it was permitted to happen without interference.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We felt very strongly that something could have been done, that the concentration camp railroads could have bombed, that some help could have been rendered that was not.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was really-- our feelings about Roosevelt, whom we had considered our savior until that time, were completely reversed [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and about Churchill and the other leaders, too.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It really became a feeling of rage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went back to-- Hella and I went back to Germany-- I forgot the exact year-- for one reason only.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wanted to look at the cemeteries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went to Nuremberg, and I had the weirdest feeling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Number one, the city has changed from when we lived there because it was bombed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was really completely destroyed and very well rebuilt, with some exceptions where suddenly a ultra-modern building stands between some very old, beautifully restored buildings.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that is immaterial.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
